snippet.title: Best VGM 1775 - Shadowrun Returns - Return of the Sixth World
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PC / Mobile
Shadowrun Returns (2013)
Return of the Sixth World
Gavin and Marshall Parker
